{
  "name": "Facial Debug",
  "docPath": "features/facial_control",
  "label": "Facial Control",
  "labels": {
    "ja": "フェイシャルコントロール",
    "zh-TW": "面部控制",
    "ko": "얼굴 제어",
    "zh-CN": "面部控制"
  },
  "description": "Provides direct sliders for facial expressions on XPS/FBX models.\r\nMouth shapes (A, I, U, E, O, Grinning, Smile 1-3, Frown), eyebrow\r\nposes (Smile, Upper, Lower, Worry, Angry 1-2), and eyelid poses\r\n(Blink, Jito, Wink, Laugh, Narrow) each get their own slider.\r\n\r\n**Use Lip Sync** drives mouth shapes from the currently playing\r\naudio. For XPS models, **Disable** turns off all facial animation,\r\nand the **Extent** sliders scale eyelid, mouth, and eyebrow\r\nmovement independently to fix over- or under-animated faces.",
  "descriptions": {
    "ja": "(Provides direct sliders for facial expressions on XPS/FBX models.\r\nMouth shapes (A, I, U, E, O, Grinning, Smile 1-3, Frown), eyebrow\r\nposes (Smile, Upper, Lower, Worry, Angry 1-2), and eyelid poses\r\n(Blink, Jito, Wink, Laugh, Narrow) each get their own slider.\r\n\r\n**Use Lip Sync** drives mouth shapes from the currently playing\r\naudio. For XPS models, **Disable** turns off all facial animation,\r\nand the **Extent** sliders scale eyelid, mouth, and eyebrow\r\nmovement independently to fix over- or under-animated faces.)",
    "zh-TW": "(Provides direct sliders for facial expressions on XPS/FBX models.\r\nMouth shapes (A, I, U, E, O, Grinning, Smile 1-3, Frown), eyebrow\r\nposes (Smile, Upper, Lower, Worry, Angry 1-2), and eyelid poses\r\n(Blink, Jito, Wink, Laugh, Narrow) each get their own slider.\r\n\r\n**Use Lip Sync** drives mouth shapes from the currently playing\r\naudio. For XPS models, **Disable** turns off all facial animation,\r\nand the **Extent** sliders scale eyelid, mouth, and eyebrow\r\nmovement independently to fix over- or under-animated faces.)",
    "ko": "(Provides direct sliders for facial expressions on XPS/FBX models.\r\nMouth shapes (A, I, U, E, O, Grinning, Smile 1-3, Frown), eyebrow\r\nposes (Smile, Upper, Lower, Worry, Angry 1-2), and eyelid poses\r\n(Blink, Jito, Wink, Laugh, Narrow) each get their own slider.\r\n\r\n**Use Lip Sync** drives mouth shapes from the currently playing\r\naudio. For XPS models, **Disable** turns off all facial animation,\r\nand the **Extent** sliders scale eyelid, mouth, and eyebrow\r\nmovement independently to fix over- or under-animated faces.)",
    "zh-CN": "(Provides direct sliders for facial expressions on XPS/FBX models.\r\nMouth shapes (A, I, U, E, O, Grinning, Smile 1-3, Frown), eyebrow\r\nposes (Smile, Upper, Lower, Worry, Angry 1-2), and eyelid poses\r\n(Blink, Jito, Wink, Laugh, Narrow) each get their own slider.\r\n\r\n**Use Lip Sync** drives mouth shapes from the currently playing\r\naudio. For XPS models, **Disable** turns off all facial animation,\r\nand the **Extent** sliders scale eyelid, mouth, and eyebrow\r\nmovement independently to fix over- or under-animated faces.)"
  },
